  <div class="centerer">
    <div class="instructions">
      <div class="title">Schedule an Event</div>
      <div class="description">
        What an exciting time it will be! Fill in the details for the event you'll be hosting. Be sure to include all the details people will want to know, such as the theme/entertainment, location, attire, etc.
